{"_id":"0F2DvO4syuUGCmS2","name":"The Wild Swans Gang - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are a band of brothers and we specialize in fighting the \nOrder’s emissaries. Thanks to the curse that has been inflicted on us, we can \ntransform into swans.\n1 Wound (for each of the 11 gang members)</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 51.","positive":"We are a band of brothers and we specialize in fighting the \nOrder’s emissaries. Thanks to the curse that has been inflicted on us, we can \ntransform into swans.\n1 Wound (for each of the 11 gang members)","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"892oeuWeILRZUSXx","name":"Goldilocks and her War Bears - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young mercenary who combines fighting \nskills with uncontrolled fury. My loyal war bears are my family \nand no one can lay a finger on me.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 59.","positive":"I am a young mercenary who combines fighting \nskills with uncontrolled fury. My loyal war bears are my family \nand no one can lay a finger on me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"D6Q9292VE7xgQHsp","name":"The Ancient Enemy - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an ancient and powerful creature. \nMy body was formed in the fires of creation and common \nweapons can do nothing against me.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 50.","positive":"I am an ancient and powerful creature. \nMy body was formed in the fires of creation and common \nweapons can do nothing against me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"E9AZlMTulO3aqGQJ","name":"The Silent - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an unscrupulous killer, I hate humanity \nand the body to which I am condemned. My voice is reduced \nto a faint whisper, which weakened my Siren powers but did \nnot take them away.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 52.","positive":"I am an unscrupulous killer, I hate humanity \nand the body to which I am condemned. My voice is reduced \nto a faint whisper, which weakened my Siren powers but did \nnot take them away.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EeihSZYSbCVwACIY","name":"The Wise Fox - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an immortal spirit \nincarnated in the body of a talking fox \nand I have always watched over human \naffairs.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 54.","positive":"I am an immortal spirit \nincarnated in the body of a talking fox \nand I have always watched over human \naffairs.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KkBBq04n9ZyzFQCC","name":"The King’s Unlikely Tailor - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an anemic young man with a body covered in scars, escorted \nand aided by my rich friend who considers me his most precious possession.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 67.","positive":"I am an anemic young man with a body covered in scars, escorted \nand aided by my rich friend who considers me his most precious possession.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NujKJNCjMzY5gZP8","name":"The Returning Wolf - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the Returning Wolf: I am bad, hungry, \nand now I am the hunter.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 65.","positive":"I am the Returning Wolf: I am bad, hungry, \nand now I am the hunter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PFMdtrnZM3JmzKwS","name":"The Periwinkle Peer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the best \nat everything I do and I must \nwin every challenge. I do not \nexcel in science and academic \nknowledge, but no one must \ndiscover this weakness of mine. I prefer to show off my \nphysical prowess and skill.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 49.","positive":"I am the best \nat everything I do and I must \nwin every challenge. I do not \nexcel in science and academic \nknowledge, but no one must \ndiscover this weakness of mine. I prefer to show off my \nphysical prowess and skill.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bBy3MwUoZ99lN8S3","name":"The Feral Musicians of Bremen - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a place full of violence and suffering, \nable to awaken the deepest fears in the souls of those who \napproach.\n64</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 64.","positive":"I am a place full of violence and suffering, \nable to awaken the deepest fears in the souls of those who \napproach.\n64","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"coHjbbWqSriiP5Qd","name":"Alfred Leaves the Talking Ghost - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a usurer of secrets, and will sell them at \na high price. If I die, I become a ghost until I am reborn in \nflesh and blood.\n61\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 61.","positive":"I am a usurer of secrets, and will sell them at \na high price. If I die, I become a ghost until I am reborn in \nflesh and blood.\n61\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"gI62s4zQcC82nBgX","name":"Orcus the Guardian - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a giant of incredible strength and repulsive \nappearance. I serve the Order as the Hunters’ Guardian and \nexecute every order to the best of my ability.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 58.","positive":"I am a giant of incredible strength and repulsive \nappearance. I serve the Order as the Hunters’ Guardian and \nexecute every order to the best of my ability.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hEHsLhmcFsGETQXO","name":"Frog Face - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a wealthy, deformed noble, using my \nresources to achieve my purposes.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 46.","positive":"I am a wealthy, deformed noble, using my \nresources to achieve my purposes.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"jvfCVi2Gz2mZLyhu","name":"Ambrose the Sorcerer known as Old Merlin - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an ancient sorcerer, my body is weak, but my magical \npower is unmatched.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 45.","positive":"I am an ancient sorcerer, my body is weak, but my magical \npower is unmatched.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pKkl8FY8EpScagyf","name":"Oakheart the Lady of the Woods - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a twisted, lonely being \nwho wanders the forests and rewards \ncompanionship and kindness with \nboons.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 63.","positive":"I am a twisted, lonely being \nwho wanders the forests and rewards \ncompanionship and kindness with \nboons.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pPHnjvg7Cp61gOza","name":"Sinbad the Traveler of a Thousand Seas - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an experienced traveler and have seen \nevery known land. I get bored easily if I’m not interested in \nwhat I’m doing.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 60.","positive":"I am an experienced traveler and have seen \nevery known land. I get bored easily if I’m not interested in \nwhat I’m doing.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pbMV5w0LDgQR3QyH","name":"The Masked Swashbuckler - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a cunning cat who can pretend to be \nhuman thanks to a magical mask. I put myself at the service \nof the highest bidder without qualms and I use my countless \nlives to get the better of every problem.\n56</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 56.","positive":"I am a cunning cat who can pretend to be \nhuman thanks to a magical mask. I put myself at the service \nof the highest bidder without qualms and I use my countless \nlives to get the better of every problem.\n56","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qsyutCeDWQr8Ezle","name":"Fire Eater the Puppeteer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled alchemist and puppet master. \nHidden within my clothes are all kinds of tools and weapons, \neach useful for disassembling and reassembling bodies, whether \nof flesh or wood.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 55.","positive":"I am a skilled alchemist and puppet master. \nHidden within my clothes are all kinds of tools and weapons, \neach useful for disassembling and reassembling bodies, whether \nof flesh or wood.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"x3IYvjNrsmo4Y6iF","name":"The Mothers of Fate - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are three sisters, we never show our real \nidentity, but we twist fate to our pleasure thanks to our \npowerful magic.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 68.","positive":"We are three sisters, we never show our real \nidentity, but we twist fate to our pleasure thanks to our \npowerful magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Dark Presence Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
